metadata.description: "SHOWSTOP!" is a song that appeals to the rockstar in all of us. It's about knowing that no matter what may happen one day when its all said and done you gotta get up and give it everything you got the next. It's about growing up and seeing the glamorous lifestyle that many of us want to live and doing everything in our power to make it happen. It begs us to fully lean into the role of the main character in our own lives and do so with every ounce of our being.
